	* All GNUmakefiles: removed GNUSTEP_CORE_SOFTWARE=YES and
	added PACKAGE_NAME=gnustep-gui.
	* GNUmakefile: Export PACKAGE_NAME to reduce chances of a problem
	if a GNUmakefile in a subdirectory is missing it.

